{
  "stem": "9168.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Just look at the defendant, to study his face-- especially eyes-- you know, to see what I could read.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the case of these doctors, these were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And their medical system, their medicine, and their research, and what they had achieved in medicine, was probably the highest, at the highest level in the world at that time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they-- I-- I-- it was so difficult for me to even understand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, when we're born with a free will, and we know right from wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And just abdicate that totally for the Fatherland-- every one of them used that term-- to build a pure-blooded German race-- this was their goal, the extermination of all people who were not too-- who were not eligible, not qualified, to be part of this super race.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That ran as a primary [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] goal through their lives and in the work that they did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There wasn't any doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I had, of course, the greatest, greatest sympathy, as we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean it was almost like an empathetic kind of suffering, just from hearing their testimony.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was so hard not to-- I mean to write.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whenever I thought I was going to be going into tears at what I was hearing, I would keep my head down, you know, as I was writing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was such a horrifying experience for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now you know, I was pretty young, 22, 21 and 22.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And most of the reporters there were in their 30s and 40s.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some were 45.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had spent years in courtrooms, wherever they worked, listening to maybe some pretty horrifying testimony-- on, you know, serial murders, or horrible murders, for example-- that I had not been subject to.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
